{"tid":1164206,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"保連奴賽前「高唱」中國國歌","createTime":"2019-05-21T02:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T02:29:20.000Z","uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1ae31af6cd39fdfd9527e3686412446976ab3a86","tid":1164206,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/61aa89/f/800x0/https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/4/284/25489181284/25606113337_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F61aa89%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F4%2F284%2F25489181284%2F25606113337_600x399.jpg&h=3a4f0ec9&s={SIZE}\" />【Now Sports-體育】被國內球迷暱稱為「暴力鳥」的廣州恒大中場荷西保連奴，上周五代表球隊於中超作客武漢卓爾時，身為巴西人的他賽前竟能跟著隊友們一起高唱中國國歌，內地網民對此擊節讚賞。<br />\n30歲的荷西保連奴（Paulinho）自2015年加盟綽號「華南虎」的廣州恒大後，多次協助這支中超班霸贏得聯賽錦標。雖然這位巴西中場在2017/18球季曾離開球隊，轉投巴塞隆拿與球王美斯合作，但1季過後，保連奴選擇重投中國足球懷抱，再次回歸簡拿華路麾下的華南虎效力。<br />\n<br />\n中超除吸引不少當打外援到國內掘金外，另一特色就是每場比賽開始前，都會奏唱中國國歌。一般來說，外藉球員都只會肅立著凝望國旗，可是保連奴於上周五球隊作客武漢卓爾的中超比賽時，就做出了令人意外的舉動。電視鏡頭拍到他在賽前竟能伴隨著《義勇軍進行曲》的旋律，以普通話與隊友們一起高唱國歌，令內地球迷無不感到驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n據保連奴的隊友透露，他早前已曾嘗試演唱國歌，但當時只會唱「前進！前進！進！」這句歌詞。然而，經過多年的浸淫，他現在掌握的歌詞數量已遠比2年前多。賽後，有國內網民在微博稱讚他是「最可愛的暴力鳥」，更有人笑指「暴力鳥已經過社會主義的洗禮」。<br />\n<br />\n看來，將來所有於中國踢球的外援球員都要如此「愛國」，才能避免重蹈去季山東魯能的巴西前鋒迪亞高泰迪利因不尊重國歌而被罰停賽的覆轍。<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/sports/player?newsId=sp25489181284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp25489181284&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbWLTbr5529Gqcy%2B2MeRGono%3D&h=aedd07a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp25489181284&h=865e26ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/sports/player?newsId=sp25489181284</a>"},{"pid":"c72a36daf308db09a6af99b843a3a77d211da9f6","tid":1164206,"uid":111996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:01:38.000Z","msg":"麻友係雞"},{"pid":"cdfd868056164f3c91e79fca3a588927153616b5","tid":1164206,"uid":199590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"f2ce1edacaf4e8e57aa21764116b8151e60e44b8","tid":1164206,"uid":127177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:10:14.000Z","msg":"做壞規矩，叫Oscar同侯克嗰班點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8731ef4a7a3099f6ecc4c469aa15742c29c0663","tid":1164206,"uid":33730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:11:43.000Z","msg":"收完錢交足戲, 呢啲演員咪專業囉"},{"pid":"50344fa0b401cd26a8579ba94be1821b2a73a64a","tid":1164206,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f2ce1edacaf4e8e57aa21764116b8151e60e44b8","tid":1164206,"uid":127177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:10:14.000Z","msg":"做壞規矩，叫Oscar同侯克嗰班點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:18:22.000Z","msg":"入鄉隨俗唔通點<br />\n我地香港人去英國都講英文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d06c0a296c3ef8d85e2585a5fae6eb071105c6","tid":1164206,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:24:18.000Z","msg":"有沒有信心"},{"pid":"7814611b40f7d2f8ec010a9e1fccac88d9ba486f","tid":1164206,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T02:29:20.000Z","msg":"巴西 = 南美支那"}]}